1.) start localstack with docker
create docker yaml file

docker-compose up

2.) bootstrap the environment
cdklocal bootstrap

3.) Create cdk project
cdklocal init app --language=csharp

4.) Create stack for s3 and deploy
cdklocal deploy --all -v

5.) Create stack for lambda exection role

6.) Push lambda package to s3

7.) Create lambda in localstack

8.) Create rest API on gateway

9.) Get restAPI Id and root resource id

	Update the POST method 
	
